snippet.title: [Black MIDI] Caramell - CARAMELLDANSEN / ｳｯｰｳｯｰｳﾏｳﾏ (ﾟ∀ﾟ) 1.12 Million
snippet.description:
Made by: Me

Black MIDI of Caramelldansen from Caramell (known currently as Caramella Girls), known to be a meme in the past, the song was originally released in 2001, later uploaded in Youtube in 2008 and became popular. Contrary to some beliefs, Caramelldansen is a Swedish song, not a Japanese song, plus the origina lyrics are in Swedish.

Reblack version by EpreTroll: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gRHCgH2WZpM

- 2008 version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zvq9r6R6QAY
